{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Privacy Policy{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
  <main class="container legal-page" aria-labelledby="privacy-title">
    <h1 id="privacy-title">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>We respect your privacy. This page explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your choices.</p>

    <h2 id="what-we-collect">Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>Contact details you provide (e.g., name, email, phone) and service preferences to connect you with a groomer.</p>

    <h2 id="how-we-use">How We Use Information</h2>
    <p>To process your inquiry, match you with a groomer, and communicate about your request. We do not sell personal data.</p>

    <h2 id="retention">Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain lead and related records only as long as needed for matching, support, fraud prevention, and legal obligations. Typical retention periods will be published here. You may request deletion at any time.</p>

    <h2 id="your-rights">Your Choices</h2>
    <p>Contact us to access, correct, or delete your information. Marketing opt-ins (if any) can be revoked at any time.</p>

    <p>For more details or requests, contact support at <a href="mailto:support@cleanwhiskers.com">support@cleanwhiskers.com</a>.</p>
  </main>
{% endblock %}

